726
00:29:37,121 --> 00:29:39,426
DAN: Poisonous pudding?
<i>Are you kidding me?</i>

727
00:29:39,429 --> 00:29:40,891
So, Simon must have gotten sick

728
00:29:40,894 --> 00:29:42,403
