778
00:31:35,578 --> 00:31:38,059
Oh, there you are.
Where'd you run off to?

779
00:31:38,062 --> 00:31:40,054
Just needed to clear my head.

780
00:31:40,056 --> 00:31:42,824
- Do you think Charlotte will be all right?
- Yeah.

781
00:31:42,826 --> 00:31:45,093
