784
00:31:49,733 --> 00:31:53,201
Yes, well... you'd be
surprised, Detective.

785
00:31:53,203 --> 00:31:54,535
Okay.

786
00:31:54,537 --> 00:31:56,871
Well, now that we
know all three suspects

787
00:31:56,873 --> 00:31:58,740
